Package org.activebpel.rt.bpel.server.engine.receive

Interface Summary
IAeBPELReceiveHandler Interface detailing the abstract methods required of pluggable receive handlers
IAeExtendedMessageContext Extended Message Context interface supporting the additional information required by our pluggable receive handlers such as those for SOAP messages, including WSRM
 

Class Summary
AeAbstractReceiveHandler Common base class for implementations of IAeReceiveHandler
AeBPELReceiveHandlerFactory A receive handler factory for the BPEL Receive handler.
AeDefaultReceiveHandler Receive handler that simply invokes the BPEL engine.
AeDelegatingReceiveHandlerFactory A receive handler factory that delegates to other factories based on the protocol in the URN.
AeExtendedMessageContext Extended Message Context supporting the additional information required by our pluggable receive handlers such as those for SOAP messages, including WSRM
AeSOAPReceiveHandler Abstract receive handler for handling input and output data as SOAPEnvelope documents
